            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Cartula de Franciano. In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anno ab
                        incarnatione eius millesimo centesimo vicegimo primo, mense martio,
                        indictione quarta Xa. Manifestus sum ego <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#people/96">Ildebrandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> filius <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/97"
                            >Raineri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>, qui professus sum lege viv[ere …] et
                            <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/98">Maximilla</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> iugales et <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissam</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/99">Lupa</persName> qualiter
                        comuniter et consentientes promittimus venerabili <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/103">Mauro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> stipulanti quod ab hac hora in antea nos, nec
                        alii per nos, nec nostri hered[es …]bimus adversus <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/78" key="#Monasteries">Sancti Quilici
                        </orgName>nec adversus suos rectores nec adversus aliquem vestro nomine
                        possidentes agemus, nominatim de medietate omnium <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terrarum</rs>, quas <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Count #Oral_grants"
                            >olim abuistis et tenuistis</rs>, vel alii per vo[s, a co]mite <persName
                            ref="#people/97">Rainerio</persName> et a <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/101">Adalasia</persName> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/89"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            >Franciano</placeName>, sicuti in ipsa cartula legitur, et finibus
                        circumdata, et etiam de medietate de ipso <rs key="#Castle">castellare</rs>.
                        Et si apparuerit ullum datum aut factum vel ali[a da]tio vel obligatio, quam
                        nos in aliquam partem fecissemus et nos inde vos defendere non potuerimus ab
                        omnibus hominibus, promittimus tibi Mauro abbati et tuis successoribus
                        stipulanti componere penam quinquaginta librarum Lucensium et post penam
                        solutam hoc pactum maneat firmum verbis subnixum, quia inter nos taliter
                        convenimus. <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">Launehild, idest meritum</rs>,
                        recipimus a te prefato abbate, ut hec obbligatio valeat et firma permaneat.
                        Actum in <placeName ref="#places/87"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Residential #Count #Itinerary"
                            >Suvereto</placeName>. Signa manuum Ildebrandi comitis et Lupe comitisse
                        et Maximille iugalis, qui queve hoc pactum verbis subnixum scribere
                        rogaverunt. Signa manuum <persName key="#Witness #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/104">Rugeri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs> filii <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildibrandi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Vulpellus">Wlpelli</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Perlus">Perli</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Berardinus">Berardini</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus/Grassus">Petri Crassi</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Malpilius">Malpilli</name></persName>
                        filii eius et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius"
                            >Rainerii</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Rufinellus"
                                >Rufinelli</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Tancredus">Tancredi</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Huguccio">Ugiccionis</name>
                            <name ref="Berardus">Berardoni</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Salarius">Salarii</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Walfredus">Walfredi</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Tremali</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wazo">Wazonis</name></persName> de <placeName>Monte
                            Liverenti</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido"
                                >Widonis</name></persName> de <placeName>Monticulo</placeName>
                        testium. Maximilla comitissa filia <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count"><name ref="Rogerius">Rogerii</name></persName>
                        confirmavit hoc in <placeName ref="#places/88"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Residential #Countess #Itinerary"
                            >Malliano</placeName>, testibus <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/104">Rugerio</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/127"
                            >Biserno</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido"
                                >Widone</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bambarinus">Banbarino</name></persName>. Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Aimerigus"
                            >Aimerigus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini
                        inperatoris post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
